dc_title_s: Chicago harbor & bar, Illinois from survey made between March 29th & April 9th 1856 under the direction of Brevet Lieut. Col. J.D. Graham, Major U.S. Top. Engineers. Superintending Engineer of Lake Michigan Works.
dc_creator_sm: Graham, J. D. (James Duncan), 1799-1865.,United States. Army. Corps of Topographical Engineers.
dc_description_s: The soundings are in feet & tenths of a foot. Includes sailings directions and description of the buildings at old Fort Dearborn. "Map G.
